programme.title: One Strange Rock E4
programme.desc: Our rock is special - it's alive. Though the building blocks of life are common across the universe, life is rare. So what is it about planet earth that sets it apart? programme.title: Nick Baker's Eco Malaysia
programme.desc: British naturalist, Nick Baker, travels to South East Asia to embark on a unique eco-adventure in the Malaysian Peninsula - one of the most bio-diverse landscapes on the planet. His journey begins in the 130 million-year-old Belum-Temengor rainforest, and then he travels to the lush valley of Lenggong to explore the caves of Gua Gunung Runtuh before trying his hand at elephant caretaking.

programme.title: Nazi Megastructures S4E2

programme.title: Wicked Tuna S7E1
programme.desc: The Gloucester, Massachusetts's bluefin tuna fishing fleet is back for another season with the biggest paydays they've ever seen and the most toxic voyages in Wicked Tuna history. FV-Tuna.Com is determined to reclaim the title of Champion of the fleet. With his returning, trusty crew, Captain Dave Carraro plans to start this season by catching the first fish and not stop until he has brought in more fish and more profit than any other boat. But, he'll have stiff competition this year fishing against the best of the best in New England. All boats are returning: as the second place finisher last season, Pinwheel is on a mission to dethrone the champion; Hot Tuna has a renewed sense of purpose, longing to shatter their lackluster reputation; Hard Merchandise is expanding its family operation with a new crew-member ready to make a profit; Wicked Pissah needs to retain and surpass its successful previous season; and Fish Hawk desperately needs to recover from an embarrassing and u.

programme.title: The Hidden Kingdoms Of China E5
programme.desc: Meet China's most affectionate and vocal monkeys in the remote, seasonal forests of Central China. These mountain forests and all who live here, experience unpredictable and harsh weather in a land that can be covered in snow for 4 months of the year. Follow the journey of a baby Golden snub-nosed monkey during the first year of her life as she learns all about her forest home and battles the elements to survive.

programme.title: Scrapyard Supercar E6
programme.desc: Ralph and his 2 teams of guerrilla mechanics take on Shane's Land Rover Discovery in a daunting hill climb.

programme.title: The Witch Doctor Will See You Now E2
programme.desc: Piers Gibbon travels to Peru to try to uncover the science and secrets behind traditional shamanic medicine. Joining Piers in the Amazon jungle are Michael Wudyka with constant shoulder and arm pain and asthma suffer Judith Owens, who experience a range of extreme treatments sourced from the jungle itself. Their mission is to cure their own medical ailments that they have struggled to fix at home.

programme.title: Wicked Tuna S7E6
programme.desc: Following a week when several boats in the fleet partnered up to improve their odds, some of these alliances are still going strong while others are coming apart at the seams. Pinwheel and Fish Hawk continue a fruitful partnership that's keeping both boats at the top of the fleet. But things aren't as smooth for Hot Tuna and Wicked Pissah, as Bubba's tendency to 'overshare' info with the rest of the fleet has Paul giving the Ott's the silent treatment. And while things are looking up for the Dot Com, engine troubles on the Hard Merchandise make them the weak link in a once-promising team-up.

programme.title: Live Free Or Die S3E2
programme.desc: There are only a few days left of deer hunting season in the Blue Ridge Mountains of North Carolina, and homesteaders Tony and Amelia need meat to get them through the cold winter. But Tony has never been deer hunting before and doesn't have the luxury of time to hone his methods. Tony is thrown right in to the hunt, and the pressure is on.

programme.title: Live Free Or Die S3E3
programme.desc: It's trapping season and frontiersman Colbert must get to work. Selling beaver pelts in town will provide him with the bulk of the money to pay the taxes on his land and purchase small items that he cannot get from the swamp. Hunter-gatherer Matt tries hunting rabbits with his new homemade bow and arrow. If he cannot get a source of protein to store for the winter he will need to leave in search of a new shelter.

programme.title: Lawless Island Alaska Compilations S2E4
programme.desc: The newest member of the community, Amanda's story illustrates how the Lawless Island community welcomes newcomers and guides them into self-sustaining Alaskans.

programme.title: One Strange Rock E5
programme.desc: Will we find life like ours on another planet? All life on Earth started as single cell bacteria and stayed like that for 2 billion years. So how did that bacteria become the complex, colorful and diverse life that's all around us? And could this happen anywhere else in the universe? Hosted by astronaut Dr. Mae Jemison.

programme.title: The Witch Doctor Will See You Now E4
programme.desc: Piers Gibbon travels to Cameroon to try to uncover the science and secrets behind traditional Cameroonian medicine. Joining Piers are anxiety sufferer Jenna Patel and Dwight Werner, who has arthritis, back pain and sleep apnea, as they experience a range of extreme treatments. They are on a mission to find a potential cure that Western medicine has been unable to provide.

programme.title: Scrapyard Supercar E7
programme.desc: Ralph and his 2 teams build scrap 4x4 cars which they then race against Shane's Mercedes X Class pick-up in a bone-jarring rock crawl.

programme.title: Facing... E6
programme.desc: From bodybuilder to blockbuster action star to comedy king and then politician, Facing Schwarzenegger explores one of the greatest immigrant success stories of our generation and gives an unabashed look at the life of Arnold Schwarzenegger, an ambitious man who followed his every dream.

programme.title: Outsiders: Living Off The Edge E1
programme.desc: In an ever-shrinking world, there are few corners of the globe that aren't connected to the grid but those places do exist for those determined enough to find them. In the underground caves of the Ozark Mountains lives Joe Ray, while Dan Burton's family live on a small island, Doc and Jeanny Leverett live in a tree house in Washington, and in the mountains of Idaho lives the nomad Bear Claw.

programme.title: Airport Security: Peru E13
programme.desc: On this episode, agents of the Antinarcotics Division of Jorge Chavez International Airport, in Lima, Peru, deal with a case of unique characteristics. In the meantime, officials face language barriers as they detain an Indonesian woman. And a passenger is carrying what seem to be adorable baby blankets, but they are really full of narcotics. At the loading docks, a shipment containing 24 jars puts the drug-detecting dogs' keen sense of smell to the test. Plus, the international flight rush hour results in 2 young passengers being detained side by side at the antinarcotics division headquarters.

With unprecedented access, we uncover what happens behind the latest top-secret facilities, and follow the development behind N division's new cutting-edge high-performance machine.

programme.title: Air Crash Investigation S17E10
programme.desc: En route to Boise, Idaho, Continental Airlines Flight 1713 is delayed on the tarmac in Denver where controllers struggle to keep departures on schedule amid heavy snow. When the plane is finally cleared for take-off, the DC-9 barely lifts off the ground before its banks sharply and crashes. Investigators find nothing wrong with the aircraft itself, but what they eventually uncover changes commercial flight forever.

programme.title: Mega Breakdown S2E3
programme.desc: In Russia's far north, the world's largest nuclear submarine, the Typhoon, is ready to be dismantled. But it is a risky mission to dismantle a submarine with nuclear reactors, remove the radioactive nuclear fuel, move the sub into a dry dock and recycle its hull.

programme.title: Car SOS S5E5
programme.desc: Tim and Fuzz have taken on a legendary 1980s French hot hatch, the mighty Renault 5 GT Turbo. The car's owner, Ben, was part way through a full restoration when he was struck down with serious organ failure meaning his beloved GT ended up an unfinished project. Can Tim and Fuzz get his dream car back on the road?

programme.title: Mega Factories: Supercars E10
programme.desc: Now with fossil fuels becoming increasingly sparse, one company is trying to change the way we commute; this is the story behind the world's first fully electric premium sedan – the Tesla Model S. Tesla's electrical experts in Fremont, CA are gearing up for mass production in a groundbreaking new Mega Factory – but will the Model S take the world by storm?

programme.title: To Catch A Smuggler: USA E7
programme.desc: A suspicious solo passenger arriving into LAX from Nigeria tells a story that doesn't quite add up. The MIA agriculture team casts a wide net, inspecting everything from raw meat to hunting trophies, eventually unearthing a massive shipment of mysterious green powder. And HSI agents at JFK have their hands full with a controlled delivery of MDMA, plus multiple food couriers suspected of importing more than just snacks within checked luggage.

programme.title: The Story Of God With Morgan Freeman S3E4
programme.desc: Sin is a part of the human condition. But can we conquer it? Morgan Freeman travels the world, from California to Italy to Vietnam, to understand how different faiths think of and deal with sin. He'll learn about the bloody Medieval practice of self-flagellation, the mysterious Sin Eaters, and the Confucian view of sin. He'll also meet a man who is trying to atone for his years as an executioner.

programme.title: Abu Dhabi, Between Tradition And 21St Century
programme.desc: The documentary also shows the ancient archaeological heritage present in Abu Dhabi. The legacy from the Stone, Iron and Bronze Ages have been preserved, and from falconry to camel racing and horse breeding, discover how these ancient practices have survived into the 21st-century, coexisting side-by-side with modern life.

programme.title: Living Free With Kimi Werner E2
programme.desc: Champion spearfisher and deep-sea diver Kimi Werner travels to the remote mountains of Northern Malaysia where she joins Ladia Kuta and his young family as they survive and thrive deep in the wilderness. Kimi braves tropical weather conditions, practices sustainable farming, foraging and fishing techniques all while forging a connection with a family that has carved a life for themselves off the beaten track.

programme.title: Wicked Tuna S9E1
programme.desc: As the season opens, Gloucester's elite get challenged by top new fishermen. Captain Bob Cook and his crew on Fat Tuna vow to dethrone reigning champion Dave Carraro on FV-Tuna.Com. Tyler on Pinwheel faces off with Krakens captain Sam Law who is out to settle a personal score, while Hot Tuna is the target of Wasabi co-captains Zack Plante and Charlie Boivin who believe they've got more grit than TJ Ott. The new contenders arrival tests the Gloucester fleet in ways they've never faced before as a heated battle for bluefin begins on the Atlantic Ocean.

programme.title: Homestay China E1
programme.sub-title: From The Grasslands To The Highlands
programme.desc: Kimi learns how the Nu people make their living harvesting and weaving bamboo. Dennis discovers Inner Mongolia where he learns how the horse is still central to life here - like the warriors of the past. Chris from New York travels to the historic town of Qikou where he joins a team of builders renovating one of Qikou's famous merchant building and he joins a company of Shadow Puppeteers.

programme.desc: Kolkata is home to India's largest Chinese community, which has been in existence for over 200 years, leaving a huge impact on the local food scene. They are fiercely proud of their Hakka-style cuisine and David can't wait to get his fill. He spends the day with a family that produces and sells their own Chinese sauce, eating their delicious momos and fried chicken.

programme.title: David Rocco's Dolce India S2E11
programme.desc: David finally fulfills his dream of visiting the Golden Temple, the holiest Sikh gurudwara in the world. The langar inside the Golden Temple, where the community comes and cooks together, serves upwards of 100,000 people a day and David gets to experience the mania of the meal preparation firsthand. Later, David takes a local food tour to sample all of the local Punjabi delicacies.

programme.title: Confucius Was A Foodie S3E4
programme.desc: The taste of Chinese medicinal herbs, bitter flavor is said to clear 'heat', strengthen the stomach, and promote salivation. Bitterness in often found in Chinese cooking, but rarely used alone. Christine cooks a popular local bitter ingredient, and makes a less than delicious visit to a Traditional Chinese Medicine shop, experiencing firsthand the power of bitter herbs.

programme.title: Around The World In 80 Dishes E5
programme.desc: Although Manu has visited Tokyo before, this time he is on his own and has a tight budget. Still, he is keen to learn and discover as much as he can. His first stop is the legendary fish market to learn about the renowned tuna sold there but he has to make it through the craziness of the Tokyo fish market first.

programme.title: Ugly House To Lovely House With George Clarke S2E3
programme.desc: Martyn and Sally are desperate to transform their totally impractical 1980's upside down house. Dominated by a big double garage this mishmash of living spaces is so badly laid out that to get from the kitchen to the garden you have to go through the master bedroom. Not ideal for a family that love to barbeque. George teams them up with innovative architect Greg Blee. Greg has recently been busy designing lavish million pound projects in the Caribbean. Can he turn his talents to something much smaller, and will he be able to create a design that works on Martyn and Sally's budget of just £65,000?

programme.title: Mega Food E1
programme.desc: Florence is about to host the Pitti Immagine Uomo, and for one local caterer that means business. Galateo Ricevimenti is renowned for their skills in turning a fashion theme into a culinary dream, but the menswear fashion show is going to test this team to the limit. Go backstage with Italian food and fashion as we enter the caterer's kitchen during one of the busiest weeks in the industry.

programme.title: Easyjet: Inside The Cockpit S1E1
programme.desc: EasyJet, the UK's biggest airline, launched its largest ever pilot recruitment drive including a focus on encouraging more women to apply for this career where females currently make only three per cent of pilots worldwide. Becoming a pilot involves dedication and determination and the trainees come from every walk of life. But does the reality live up to the dream of flying high?

programme.title: Island Hunter E4
programme.desc: Puerto Rico is one of the most popular vacation destinations for Americans, and it's easy to see why; everyone speaks English, it's easy to get to, and of course, it's still a part of the US! Host Liesel Hlista starts off her journey with a goal to feel at one with herself and the best way to do that is with a stint of yoga, atop a paddleboard. SUP yoga! Feeling centered, she begins exploring the island by taking a very detailed walking historical tour as well as a food tour. Bouncing around cantinas and trying out slushy drinks made with the local Don Q rum, Liesel gets a unique insight into old San Juan. To step up the action, Liesel also explores all the hands-on activities such as riding horseback on the beach, riding ATV's through the muddy swamps, and hiking through the super lush El Yunque rainforest. Luxurious resorts are only a stone's throw away - hopping islands, Liesel gets to experience the ultra modern and chic El Blok located in Vieques. Between stays at all th.

programme.title: Easyjet: Inside The Cockpit S1E2

programme.title: Island Hunter E5
programme.desc: Hong Kong is Asia's world city and this episode is a complete 360 from the melee of tropical island paradises. Hong Kong is famous for it's skyscraper strewn skyline and in this episode, local girl Lesley Chiang is on a mission to show a different side of Hong Kong. Her journey starts off in Hong Kong bay where she gets a taste of the 5 star life at the Ritz Carlton. Pampering at the 108th floor spa, dining at Michelin 2 star rated Ting Lung Heen, and beyond! Lesley checks out the art scene of Soho, and PMQ, an establishment geared towards Hong Kong's budding arts and crafts talent. At night time, local nightlife expert Johannes Pong shows Lesley the wild side of town as they bounce around the latest bars and clubs. When it's time to chow, Jowett Yu, a rising star in the culinary world shows Lesley his favorite hometown hang outs; roast geese to yummy sea food bites. Taking a break from Hong Kong island, Lesley also checks out the nearby Lantau island where she gets a taste o.

Now the islands' guardians reveal the hidden patterns of these endangered creatures with latest technology, and gain the critical insights needed to save them.

programme.desc: Chef Ramsay travels to the Island of Maui, Hawaii, to explore the secrets of Hawaiian cuisine along the rugged Hana coastline.

programme.desc: Kolkata, the first stop of Pablo's journey and the gastronomical capital of India. programme.title: Gourmet Goes Tribal E2
programme.desc: Monpa tribe- the other half of Brokpas are the farmers who reside in this small, beautiful village of Dirang. Always in barter with the Brokpas, Monpas people are farmers who grow a lot of corn.

programme.title: Gourmet Goes Tribal E3
programme.desc: Reaching out to the most remote parts of Arunachal Pradesh, Pablo stepped foot on one of the far-flung valleys of Arunachal- The Lubrang Valley. Sheltering the Brokpa tribe and their yaks, Lubrang comes with very unpredictable weather. What kept Pablo warm at such high altitude is some delectable yak food and hospitality of the warmhearted Brokpas.

programme.desc: In today's Asian adventure John Torode finds himself in the bustling metropolis of Hong Kong looking for traditional dishes to delight his pallet. John's first stop is the Long Kwai Fong district where he explores the markets with new friend Silvana. Spurred on by the potential for healthy eating, John is taken to an eatery that claims to improve your chances for a long life.

programme.title: United Plates Of America E7
programme.desc: After the Vietnam War ended in 1975, many Vietnamese people migrated to California, much of them settling in San Francisco. In this episode we meet several Vietnamese immigrants, learn about their journey to America and tastes their amazing authentic Vietnamese food.

programme.title: Extreme China E2
programme.desc: Ben explores China's southern sea with Dou Dou, a free diver who is one of the first to free dive under ice in Tibet. Ben and Dou Dou journey to Hainan's fishing village to learn sea-born survival skills from unique groups of fishermen. The duo learn a trick of fishing potion from a group of free diving fishermen and a trade of night fishing from fishermen who live on boats for generations before they set off on stand up paddleboards for an ocean adventure. They explore the open sea, free dive and spear fish, hoping to bring in the biggest catch possible.

programme.title: Access 360 World Heritage S2E8
programme.desc: Beneath the ancient castles and cathedrals of Prague is a hidden underworld that traces the story of this World Heritage through the ages. But time and the forces of nature are threatening to destroy what's survived for over a thousand years. Now, teams of explorers, engineers and master craftsmen must go inside Prague's secret spaces to safeguard its cherished heritage.

programme.title: Ultimate Airport Dubai S1E5
programme.desc: This episode features an emergency in air traffic control that leads to a runway closure, a huge task to re-number every departure gate in the airport while it is operational, and the mounting tension on the building site of a new $3.2 billion terminal extension, which is built specifically to accommodate the A380, the world's biggest passenger airliner.

programme.title: Late Nite Eats S1E2
programme.desc: Jordan explores the Montreal scene and it doesn't disappoint. First, he heads to Notre Dame de Grace to try the late night discount menu at Monkland Tavern. Jordan falls in love with the braised calamari caponata, but his mind is blown by the many flavors in the soft shell crab banh mi.

programme.title: Route Awakening S4E1

programme.title: John Torode's Asia E5
programme.desc: John Torode begins his exploration of Hong Kong's modern cuisine with an introduction to Cha Chang Teng for breakfast where eastern and western cultures clash on a plate. programme.title: Gourmet Goes Tribal E9

programme.title: Easyjet: Inside The Cockpit S1E3

programme.title: Memoir Of A Murderer

programme.title: The Spies
programme.desc: Kim, seorang mata-mata Korea Utara yang telah tinggal di Korea Selatan selama 22 tahun tiba-tiba dihubungi oleh atasannya. Mereka berencana untuk menyelesaikan misi sebelumnya dan mencuri uang simpanan target sebanyak-banyaknya.

programme.title: Forbidden Dream
programme.desc: Dua penemu Korea menjalin hubungan selama 20 tahun sembari memajukan bidang astronomi.

programme.title: Spellbound
programme.desc: Yeo-Ri dapat melihat hantu dan kejadian aneh yang terjadi di sekitarnya. Jo-Goo menawarkan bantuan saat ia bergabung dengan pertunjukan sulapnya sebelum para hantu menjauhkannya dari hidup Yeo-Ri.

programme.title: Rampant
programme.desc: Setelah bebas dari penjara di luar negeri, seorang pangeran dan rekannya bekerjasama untuk memerangi iblis yang haus darah di zaman Korea kuno.

programme.title: Heung-boo: The Revolutionist
programme.desc: Sebuah sandiwara jalanan menjadi populer pada masa Dinasti Joseon. Heung-boo, sang penulis naskah, banyak diincar oleh para elit politik yang ingin menggunakan ketenarannya untuk kepentingan mereka sendiri.

programme.title: The Pension
programme.desc: Saat empat pasangan berbeda pergi ke sebuah motel dengan alasan yang berbeda pula, segala kebenaran dan rahasia pun terungkap.

programme.title: Lost And Found
programme.desc: Ji-ho diam-diam jatuh cinta pada pria yang sama selama 10 tahun terakhir. Saat ia tertabrak mobil sang pria, ia berbohong demi menjadi dekat dengannya, namun justru berakhir dengan bencana.

programme.title: Lump Of Sugar
programme.desc: Seorang gadis sangat sedih saat sahabatnya, seekor kuda, dijual. Namun, saat mereka bertemu lagi dua tahun kemudian, keduanya berkesempatan untuk membuat keajaiban dengan bekerjasama dalam sebuah perlombaan.

programme.title: The Scam
programme.desc: Hyeon-Soo bergabung dengan tim elit yang dibentuk oleh seorang gangster yang menyamar menjadi seorang investor untuk melakukan penipuan terbesar demi mendapatkan 60.000.000 dolar dari pasar saham.

programme.title: RV: Resurrected Victims
programme.desc: Suatu hari, ibu jaksa Jin-hong yang sudah meninggal kembali ke rumah dan mencoba membunuhnya. Ia pun segera menjadi tersangka utama atas pembunuhan ibunya.

programme.title: Truck
programme.desc: Seorang sopir truk tak sengaja melihat pembunuhan oleh sebuah geng. Ia bersedia membantu membuang mayat-mayat itu agar tetap dibiarkan hidup. Namun, situasi memburuk ketika seorang pembunuh berantai menumpang truknya.

programme.title: Miss Granny
programme.desc: Berbagai masalah dan kekacauan terjadi ketika seorang nenek berusia 70 tahun yang tidak akur dengan keluarga putranya secara ajaib kembali menjadi dirinya saat berumur 20 tahun.

programme.title: Inside Men
programme.desc: Seorang mantan antek politik berusaha membalas dendam usai dijatuhkan oleh seorang politisi kejam di kala sesosok penyelidik yang gigih berusaha menemukan bukti adanya hubungan di antara keduanya.

programme.title: Train To Busan
programme.desc: Saat virus-zombie melanda Korea Selatan, para penumpang termasuk seorang ayah dan putrinya, pasangan saumi istri, dan beberapa siswa berjuang untuk bertahan hidup dalam kereta api dari Seoul ke Busan.

programme.title: The Divine Fury
programme.desc: Setelah terbangun dengan luka misterius di tangannya, seorang petinju mendapati dirinya bertarung melawan kekuatan jahat yang menyebabkan malapetaka di bumi.

programme.title: The Odd Family: Zombie On Sale
programme.desc: Keluarga Park yang aneh mencoba mengambil keuntungan dari sebuah eksperimen ilegal perusahaan farmasi yang secara tidak sengaja menciptakan zombie.

programme.desc: Sebuah kisah tentang seorang prajurit Korea Utara yang bergabung dalam kelompok tari tap bernama Swing Kids di kamp tahanan Geoje semasa Perang Korea.
